        "Id": "ab34c4db-4bc7-4e7a-982b-302a7b8922dd",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "The Ballad of Agent 47",
        "Location": "LOCATION_ELEGANT_LLAMA",
        "PublicId": "131367179150",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/elegant/scene_llama.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 26631f97-44f0-4d37-be99-425df5ff9144).Image",
        "Description": "Our client is Sara Berry, a young woman who wants to be Prom Queen. She has asked us to eliminate 5 of her potential rivals.  For an extra challenge, she requests that you eliminate the targets in order. Furthermore,  the 1st target must be eliminated with a poisoned drink, the 2nd by falling on rocks, the 3rd diced with a kitchen knife and marinated in the large freezer, the 4th quietly drowned, and the final target cut to pieces with the garden shedder. Good luck 47.",
